Joust Language Specification
-----------------------------
New Name For Program: Needle.ChessGame.Found
A valid program can search for:
1) A particular board
2) A sequence of boards

Also want nice graphs and stats
Highlighting around chess pieces that are in check, defended, safe, canAttack

Sample valid Joust programs:
exists(K)
exists(K) through sameFile(Q, q) until checkmate
